{"tid":2136113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"成功不必靠父幹！他們明明有強大的家庭背景，卻要靠自己，闖出屬於自己的路！","createTime":"2020-08-02T01:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T06:03:04.000Z","uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f34d07eacaaa5a6b8829f4c8213d191979bf7dcf","tid":2136113,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.topbeautyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Screen-Shot-2019-04-30-at-12.34.14-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.topbeautyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FScreen-Shot-2019-04-30-at-12.34.14-PM.png&h=a8d71025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在人人都說成功要靠父幹，但偏偏有些人，明明可以靠家裡，但卻要用實力去證明自己，贏得大家的讚賞。在他們的故事裡，沒有父幹，只有苦幹。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.topbeautyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Screen-Shot-2019-04-30-at-12.31.34-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.topbeautyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FScreen-Shot-2019-04-30-at-12.31.34-PM.png&h=c04fe0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賭王的兒子何猷君，家族身家過百億，想靠家裡過日子絕對沒問題。可是天生有志氣的何猷君並沒有選擇走這一條路。天資聰敏的他入讀了美國一級學府麻省理工大學，不睡不吃，只為比其他同學提早一年畢業，而且成績也不差。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.topbeautyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Screen-Shot-2019-04-30-at-12.29.02-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.topbeautyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FScreen-Shot-2019-04-30-at-12.29.02-PM.png&h=d5c63dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畢業後，母親給了他一堆可以接手的項目，但他卻拒絕了，決心靠自己創業。他隻身跑到上海，用了一個手袋的價錢從零開始創業。創業期間被發現只是坐經濟艙，在上海坐地鐵，生活得很低調。直到上年年末，他的公司上市，成功證明靠自己依然可以闖出一片天。"},{"pid":"2449281307d50a58edd7eb75894e7be58ff73702","tid":2136113,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14e6a91099e749881f275dcabf45b21cba1a23","tid":2136113,"uid":111814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"蔡家贊都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1344f9086d36816a60a1e791264b373744544ffc","tid":2136113,"uid":175540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"用了一個手袋的價錢從零開始創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bf729c2929606ae7e0aa9d1828d3c9d978f8aa","tid":2136113,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:42:18.000Z","msg":"我都想有個媽媽支持我開公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0652744f8deea6fd259df69f10caae4c9489a05","tid":2136113,"uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲有咩說話好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07103011fb1b276391ac7b4b55f3d0feda2aab1","tid":2136113,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"🤣🤣"},{"pid":"ebc31868fb6a45b771c26f2e3b623692740c3cbf","tid":2136113,"uid":297997,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"不睡不吃<br />\n<br />\n但係日日比錢叫人做功課<br />\n<br />\n自己就對草屌女"},{"pid":"2923c8a9a5403c8dcddf66b8d5a7ae5f218c48b5","tid":2136113,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:16:16.000Z","msg":"一個BIRKIN手袋的價錢？😳🤔"},{"pid":"c1c630f932a95c906768d81676d8c4482d3e21df","tid":2136113,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"有冇5千蚊先  <br />\n<br />\n講真，四五千話多唔多話少唔少，我建議你上大陸搞生意，香港已經冇咩發展空間喇。"},{"pid":"74a5ae18c5aa2b39603e6a5c312c820fcef9fb2d","t